#lg M	kirugu


@(181-183=c224.M.181) How long will the brickwork strain its eyes upwards in tears and lamentations? Even now your lord, the Great Mountain @wDN{Enlil}, supreme in the universe, has removed lamentation from your brick buildings and made favourable your humour!

@(184-192=c224.M.184) Now, city, your lord who has had compassion and mercy for you, Father @wDN{Enlil}, lord of all countries, who has commanded that you be restored, and the great mother @wDN{Ninlil}, who entreated him in prayer there, and the brickwork itself which said to him @q[E-kur,Enlil]{“Steady the trembling of @wSN{Nibru}!” and said to him @q[E-kur,Enlil]{“Rebuild my women's quarters for me! Re-establish my temples for me!” -- he who mulled things over so that he came to a decision about them, @wDN{Enlil}, who found agreeable his command of true words, who beneficently entered the true temple which had suffered destruction -- he himself is removing what he turned upon you in distress.

@(193-200=c224.M.193) Just as he silenced you, when he made joy enter again he decreed as your fate the sound of choice beer and syrup being poured out to overflowing. @q[Enlil,Nippur]{“Enough! It is time to stifle the lament” he said to you himself. Because you have been living in a state of neglect, @wDN{Enlil} who has decreed your fate has said @q[Enlil,Nibru]{“My city, you have placated my sacred heart towards you.” He has returned to you! @q[Enlil,Nibru]{“Nibru, you have placated my sacred heart towards you.” He has returned to you! True city, he has decreed your great fate and made your reign long! @wSN{Nibru}, he has decreed your great fate and made your reign long!

@(201-210=c224.M.201) @wDN{Enlil} himself has commanded @wRN{Išme-@wDN{Dagan}} that the @wTN{E-kur} should shine like the day! Steady sunlight shines into the @wTN{Ki-ur}; he has brought daylight in there again for you! @wDN{Ninlil} has decreed your fate in the @wTN{Ŋaŋiššua}! @wDN{Enlil} and @wDN{Ninlil} together founded daises in the @wTN{E-kur}! They dined there and enjoyed choice beer! They deliberated how to make the black-headed people secure in their dwellings! They have brought back to you the people who had been completely devastated! They have gathered back together the children whom they turned away from their mothers! The populace goes with you in their strongholds! Shrine @wSN{Nibru}, the Great Mountain @wDN{Enlil} has returned to you!

#trailer rubric	kirugu


@(211=c224.M.211) 7th @fsux{kirugu
}

