#lg O	kirugu


@(214-219=c224.O.214) Even now, they command @wRN{Išme-@wDN{Dagan}} that @wGN{Sumer} and @wGN{Akkad} should be restored at your feet, that their scattered people should be returned to their nests! They have brought the news that the magnificent rites of @wSN{Eridug} would not be forgotten, its heart sending forth wisdom, so that good sense should be allotted! The @wDN{Anuna}, the lords who decree fates, order that @wSN{Adab} should be rebuilt, the city whose lady fashions living things, who promotes birthing!

@(220-227=c224.O.220) @wDN{An} and @wDN{Enlil} have advised that @wSN{Urim} should be restored, founded in a pasture, its divine powers distinct from the rest! They command the prince of the city @wSN{Larsam}, the herald of the universe, the judge of the numerous people, to secure its foundations, to follow the proper path! They have taken a decision concerning @wSN{Unug}-@wSN{Kulaba}, the sacred city, the handiwork of the gods, and restored it. They have brought news of the removal of all foes and enemies from the region of @wSN{Zabalam}, the city where the mistress of heaven concentrated her forces.

@(228-235=c224.O.228) @wDN{An} and @wDN{Enlil} have looked with their beneficent gaze on @wSN{Lagaš}, the mooring-pole of heaven, and the shrine @wSN{Ŋirsu}, established long ago. They have removed the treacherous @wGN{Tidnum} from that temple in @wSN{Umma}, @wTN{Šeg-kuršaga}, which had been ill treated! It is the great gods who have commanded that the foundations of @wSN{Kiš} should be secured, at the edge of @wGN{Sumer} and @wGN{Akkad}, its dominion superlative! @wSN{Marda}, the city in whose river water flows, in whose fields is fine grain -- the @wDN{Anuna} who took those things away from it returned them to it again!

@(236-243=c224.O.236) @wSN{Isin}, the provisioner of the @wDN{Anuna}, rising high since times of old -- @wDN{An}, @wDN{Enlil}, @wDN{Enki} and @wDN{Ninmaḫ} have made its reign long! By their command they have handed it over and expressed their approval! They have entrusted it to @wDN{Ninurta}, the champion, the strong hero! They have told @wDN{Ninisina}, the exalted child of @wDN{An}, the incantation priest of the Land, to rest calmly in her sacred dwelling, @wTN{Egal-maḫ}! They have told @wDN{Damu}, the chief barber of @wDN{Nunamnir}, healer of the living, to make the foreign countries bow at the feet of his father and mother!

